7581:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV1: ETRP Prescaler OFF.
7582:Drivers/STM32F1xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f1xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV2: ETRP frequency divided by 2.
